            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726497",
        "quote": "There is universal consensus among experts that the earth's atmosphere is heating up - and that we are responsible for it by putting carbon dioxide in the atmosphere. We also know that the consequences of global warming are catastrophic. But how do we make sure that all countries reduce greenhouse gases?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Eric Maskin",
            "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726497"
