    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726462",
        "quote": "What we mean by an outcome will naturally depend on the context. Thus, for a government charged with delivering public goods, an outcome will consist of the quantities provided of such goods as intercity highways, national defense and security, environmental protection, and public education together with the arrangements by which they are financed.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Eric Maskin",
            "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726462"
