        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726467",
        "quote": "I think I have met nearly all the Laureates in Economics. Among the few I haven't met, I suppose I'd most like to meet Ronald Coase because of his legendary power to persuade his colleagues of the validity of the Coase Theorem.",
