    {
        "url": "/quotes/eric_maskin_726457",
        "quote": "At Tenafly High, I was lucky to have some dedicated teachers; I'm especially indebted to my calculus instructor, Francis Piersa, who opened my eyes to the striking beauty of mathematics.",
